snippet.title: Gaze Into Fate - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gaze Into Fate - Official Gameplay Trailer

‚Gaze Into Fate‘ is a relaxing and story-driven puzzler, where you have to find your place in a world of endless wars. It's will be released on holiday 2022 for Windows PCs & Android devices. 

Learn more about our game at: ► Web: https://ikouyo.rocks/gaze-into-fate
